name: About:blank Foxkeh - Front
description:
For all you Foxkeh lovers out there!

This is just a simple Foxkeh about:blank style I've made.  The background color is a dark red color, and it shows a large picture of Foxkeh on the right-hand side of the screen.

UPDATE: Converted the image to a base64 URI format -- Foxkeh didn't want to load all the time before.  Also a new image. :D
EDIT: If Foxkeh doesn't want to load up when you first loaded up your Firefox, close the browser and re-open it, Foxkeh should then reappear.
